---
canonical:
  title: I like you, bamboo
  author: Kim Kwang-Wuk
  text: |
    I like you, bamboo,
    You are a true friend.
    When I was young,
    I played on stilts with you;

    Now that I am old, you stand outside my window
    Waiting till I need a walking stick.
korean:
   title: 대막대 너를 보니
   author: 김광욱
   language: kor
   source: https://m.blog.naver.com/kwank99/30110930003
   text: |
     대막대 너를 보니 유신(有信)하고 반갑고야.
     나니 아이 적에 너를 타고 다니더니,
     이제란 창 뒤에 섰다가 날 뒤세우고 다녀라.

